{"tid":1692323,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"窗邊鳩嗌必須立即重新開始，主力狙擊CCTVB，即時反擊！","createTime":"2019-11-04T04:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T12:27:41.000Z","uid":34241,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff176aa58c23aa229beb7d6bc7e2121c9eb173f","tid":1692323,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:30:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>時間</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n定時可以由夜晚9點鐘開始嗌，<br />\n大家幾把聲接力，嗌到10點半<br />\n<br />\n另一個突發時間係<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>每日既新聞提要時間</ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>佢播假新聞，<br />\n我地就嗌真新聞反擊</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>新聞提要<br />\n一至五(港股交易日)：11:35-11:40, 15:13-15:15<br />\n每日：20:45-20:50, 21:45-21:50<br />\n六、日：22:45-22:50</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>內容</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n夜晚：全力狙擊CCTVB，嗌口號，做當日假新聞總結<br />\n日頭：可以睇住CCTVB新聞黎嗌 (忍辱負重開台睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，LIVE反擊，佢講邊個point做假，我地就嗌返個事實出黎<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>即時反擊！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>注意</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n切忌加入粗口、過份憤怒既情緒<br />\n鳩嗌目的係動搖睇緊CCTVB既人既思緒<br />\n盡量用一個平常人既口吻，<br />\n當自己係新聞報導員咁講新聞，學下語氣，<br />\n<br />\n聽眾係普通人，唔好學長毛式叫駡<br />\n唔係直接叫人投入抗爭<br />\n呢一次鳩嗌係要狙擊CCTVB<br />\n唔好講粗口，好多普通人一聽到粗口就唔再理你噏乜，大家忍下口<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>重點</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n窗邊鳩嗌=遍地開花<br />\n我要全香港每一家每一戶，有電視，有窗既單位都要聽到你把聲<br />\n咁樣比網上媒體，FB IG YT更加入屋<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB用大氣電波侵略香港<br />\n我地就用聲音還擊！<br />\n每一棟樓都要聽到反擊CCTVB假新聞既聲音，<br />\n嗌比成個屋邨知！<br />\n<br />\n即時反擊要用大聲公！<br />\n10點鳩嗌可以預先錄定音 用喇叭播！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過留意有冇煩膠投訴<br />\n有冇可疑人士係樓下觀察，<br />\n閂窗拉簾唔好凸個頭出去，<br />\n自己大門加隔音 擋一擋，<br />\n監視埋門外有冇可疑人士遊盪，<br />\n避免比恐怖份子pinpoint入屋劫殺！"},{"pid":"fe1330fe63b6c0177336eb37fbe57315c76f38f9","tid":1692323,"uid":73000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:36:36.000Z","msg":"叫啲咩"},{"pid":"8a230615ed39aeb3a071dd3b4b26e60ed7b10e23","tid":1692323,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:46:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e4a255a8f1b81e5f1f1bdcb0312d3f3ac4fc224","tid":1692323,"uid":331682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:47:11.000Z","msg":"TVB老闆買TVB返來唔係為咗賺錢的"},{"pid":"60323e2d953c624f0cb49cdd9f4c2431adb97859","tid":1692323,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:51:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>真新聞窗邊報導員要人！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3bbe9a8ecb33f7f80ce67ba0d4173ca57f6f2b3b","tid":1692323,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:54:59.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f3ae157cb5ee4d8dd9bd24b1501427444c81de3b","tid":1692323,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:56:35.000Z","msg":"習曱甴<br />\n曱甴平<br />\n甴近平"},{"pid":"77145443426e62e9c0e962d7b7245e9fc432d5d1","tid":1692323,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:24:40.000Z","msg":"要人！"},{"pid":"4f1a35cf60d3245286052a3332f883888f1b8962","tid":1692323,"uid":298585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89b80ff8fc3c134f5f0750278cf4442d7fcbde35","tid":1692323,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f1a35cf60d3245286052a3332f883888f1b8962","tid":1692323,"uid":298585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:35:16.000Z","msg":"中間可以夾幾句呢種呼籲<br />\n主體係講返個事實出黎<br />\n<